<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's the former Home and Away actress known for her sensational bikini body.</p>

<p>And on Tuesday, Pia Miller was in the gym working hard at maintaining her physique, with motivational help from personal trainer Jono Castano Acero.</p>

<p>The 36-year-old stunner shared a video to Instagram of herself working up a sweat on an AirBike machine.</p>

<p>Getting ready for summer! Ex-Home and Away star Pia Miller was in the gym working hard at maintaining her physique on Tuesday</p>

<p>Projected on the wall in front of Pia was a photo of the actress in bikini from 2018, which originally featured her son Isaiah alongside her, but he was cropped out.</p>

<p>In the video, Jono called the image 'motivation' as Pia peddled furiously before completing her circuit.</p>

<p>'He tortures me,' the Bite Club star later said of her workout session on Instagram.</p>

<p>Bicycle workout: Projected on the wall in front of Pia was a photo of the actress in bikini from 2018, which originally featured her son Isaiah alongside her, but he was cropped out</p>

<p>Throwback: This is the original photo, featuring Isaiah (right), which Pia used as inspiration</p>

<p>Pia has been training at Jono's gym in Sydney for the past couple of weeks, and has been sharing images from their sessions.</p>

<p>The Chilean-born model recently reunited with her multi-millionaire boyfriend, Patrick Whitesell, when he visited Sydney earlier this month.</p>

<p>The couple were together for just over a week, before Hollywood agent Patrick flew back to the U.S. on a private jet about a fortnight ago. </p>

<p>Sweating it out: Pia has been training at personal trainer Jono Castano Acero's gym in Sydney for the past couple of weeks, and has been sharing images from their sessions</p>

<p>Gym buddies: Jono (right) trains many celebrity clients, including comedian Rebel Wilson</p>

<p>Pia and Patrick went public with their romance at a Halloween party in Los Angeles in October last year. It's believed they've been dating since May 2019.</p>

<p>The couple made their red carpet debut when they attended the Oscars together in February this year.</p>

<p>Before dating the super-agent, she was previously engaged to Australian filmmaker and businessman Tyson Mullane, 32.</p>

<p>Short and sweet: The Chilean model recently reunited with her millionaire boyfriend, Patrick Whitesell, when he visited Sydney earlier this month. They were together for just over a week, before Hollywood agent Patrick flew back to the U.S. on a private jet about a fortnight ago</p>
